title: East Facing 2 bedroom unit with off-street parking included
map_address: 3212 Fremont Ave S near W 32nd St
app_fee: $35.00 (Credit, criminal, income and rental history verifications)
posting_body: ['I have a wonderfully located 2 bedroom unit in a small building in Uptown on 32nd St. and Fremont Ave.', 'This unit is about 800 square feet and is on the 2nd level.', 'It is available for October 1st.', ' The rent on this unit is $1,275.00 and our base deposit is $500.', 'Both Bedrooms are carpeted.', 'The unit has hardwood floors in the living room and kitchen.', 'The bedrooms are about 12 x 12, have ceiling fans and have ample closet space with mirrored closet doors.', 'These units have a large picture window in the living room with new window treatments.', 'There is a lot of natural light.', 'I pay for the heat and water for the building and you would be responsible for your own electric.', 'There is a wall A/C in each apartment and a gas stove.', 'There are 2 reserved off street parking spots in the back of the building included in the price of the rent.', 'There is laundry in the building and a storage unit', 'To arrange a showing, please e-mail, text or call me (Bryan) at', 'show contact info', 'and I will return your message as soon as possible.', 'Please make sure to note the address, 3212, in your message.', 'We do not accept pets in the building.']
